thread.title: Kathy O'Connor
thread.title_full: White Mountain Puzzles reviewed by Kathy O'Connor

author: Kathy O'Connor
title: Kathy O'Connor
text:
These puzzles lock together excellently. I enjoyed doing the first one, and am looking forward to doing the others that I purchased.
Great, vivid colors. So much fun putting challenging puzzles together and framing them for our country log house walls.
